condition.narrative: For the purposes of Section 5.08(c) of the General Conditions, the report on the execution of the Project and related planrequiredpursuant to that Section shall be furnished to the Bank
The Borrower shall enter into agreements with power suppliers or relevant provinces, satisfactory to the Bank to ensure adequateelectric power supply for the electric traction on the Liu-Zhan railway
The Borrower shall furnish a report intergrating the results of the monitoring and evaluation activities on the progress
The Borrower shall furnish to the Bank for commments & recoommendations of the studies carired out in the preceding year
The Borrower shall prepare action plans for implementation of the recommendations of the studies carried out in the precedingyear, taking into account the comments of the Bank on such recommendation
